# 2026-04-20-smoke



## S is for Smoke

Thought a little 4-20 subject would be fun. I was trying to think, back in college and earlier what
I used to get up to on this day and honestly, I can't remember. Joke or not it cracked me up. So what
was my favorite thing to watch.

* Fairies) - This film is up there with 'Wizards' for its awesome weirdness
=> https://www.wikiwand.com/en/Faeries_(1981_film Fairies

* The GrooveTube - Chevy Chases first film I think
=> https://www.wikiwand.com/en/The_Groove_Tube The GrooveTube


Ive watched other things like half baked, chech and chong and honestly those were all really good. But
what always had me tripping back in the day was [Animusic](https://www.youtube.com/@animusic)


